<para style="p">A psalm, a song for the Sabbath day.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />It is a good thing to give thanks to Yahweh</para>

<para style="q1">and to sing praises to your name, Most High,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />to proclaim your covenant faithfulness in the morning</para>

<para style="q1">and your truthfulness every night,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />with a harp of ten strings</para>

<para style="q1">and with the melody of the lyre.</para>
